Welcome to the Fontana Dental Group! You will find we are proud to provide quality dental care for patients of all ages. Our first goal is to help you experience exceptional oral hygiene. Whether general or cosmetic, we want your smile looking amazing. You always come first! Whether you need affordable low-cost care or flexible scheduling, we will work with you to make sure everything is covered. You will understand your dental needs, and we will work with you to get that brilliant smile back. We are proud to offer you specialty dental work as well. Our practice is proud to employ specialists such as endodontics, pediatric dentists, and oral surgeons are available! Need a periodontist or orthodontist? We will set you up. We are proud to offer evening and same-day appointments! If you would like to schedule an appointment, just contact us today and we will get you set up! Most insurance plans and Denti-Cal are accepted as payment forms. Fontana Dental Group has been serving the Inland Empire area since 1965. We are known for providing a professional, comfortable and caring environment for all of our patients. We aim to take care of all your dental care needs at an affordable rate. Dr. Andrew Lubczuk has been serving the area since 1991. He graduated from Loma Linda University and practices cosmetic dentistry, general dentistry, periodontics, and endodontics. In addition, he won a professional award for general dentistry. Along with being well-educated and experienced, Dr. Lubczuk focuses on both educating and communicating with his patients. He believes that this is the best way to help patients develop excellent oral hygiene. Whether you need general teeth cleaning or root canal treatments, our staff is ready to help. We offer evening and same-day appointments! If you would like to schedule an appointment, contact us today! Most insurance plans and Denti-Cal are accepted. Whatever your specific dental needs, we will help you find an exceptional and affordable solution to getting it taken care of. We are proud to provide pediatric dental care for all of your children. We delight in helping your little ones get the amazing smile that reflects the beauty of their inside on the outside! Saturday - by appointment only.
